title: Funkadelic - The Whole Funk / Definitive Funkadelic 1976 - 1981
description:
A superb set covering the late '70s output of George Clinton's ground-breaking funk powerhouse, featuring tracks from the four albums that Funkadelic put out on Warner Brothers between 1976 and 1981, as well as including live versions of "Cosmic Slop" and "Maggot Brain" , and instrumental versions of "One Nation Under a Groove" and "Electric Spanking of War Babies."
An eclectic mix of funk, off-the-wall humor, and rock.
